 thủ cũ là Naevia, Crixus, Gannicus và Agron trở thành các tướng nổi dậy, tham gia cùng Spartacus trong cuộc chiến chống lại đế chế. Thượng viện La Mã quay sang một chính trị gia và quân nhân tàn nhẫn, Marcus Crassus, để hạ bệ nô lệ. Crassus nhận một ngôi sao trẻ đang lên - Julius Caesar - làm đồng minh.</p>","tmdb":{"type":"tv","id":"46296","season":3,"vote_average":8.03,"vote_count":2818},"modified":"2023-04-15T01:45:29.000Z","cast":["Liam McIntyre","Manu Bennett","Dustin Clare","Cynthia Addai-Robinson","Jaime Murray","Ellen Hollman","Luna Rioumina","Marisa Ramirez","Ditch Davey","Barry Duffield","Pana Hema-Taylor","Stephen Lovatt","Blessing Mokgohloa","Jenna Lind","Hanna Mangan Lawrence"],"director":[],"cast_meta":[{"name":"Liam McIntyre","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Liam McIntyre","tmdb_id":934219,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/vTw11F1awNW8AlxInljEsK96cNB.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/934219"},{"name":"Manu Bennett","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Manu Bennett","tmdb_id":41782,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/vwcTCQoRqfOjGZA1TPCx9TWTNht.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/41782"},{"name":"Dustin Clare","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Dustin Clare","tmdb_id":220916,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/3F2pmjmi7CnUELSq613ifLekYx1.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/220916"},{"name":"Cynthia Addai-Robinson","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Cynthia Addai-Robinson","tmdb_id":182272,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/fgXXRWLRDprVH9Bf2et0zRLk7HQ.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/182272"},{"name":"Jaime Murray","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Jaime Murray","tmdb_id":1223059,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/viqfbECKPLI8nRO6sya8YFu8yc2.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1223059"},{"name":"Ellen Hollman","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Ellen Hollman","tmdb_id":83218,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ebNqpUF7WFr4lhP6FhT9O1doc8q.jpg","t